um crystal pieces — substantially below equivalent US retail prices. Custom engraving in English, Hindi, Gujarati, Tamil, Telugu, Malayalam, and Punjabi script is included at no extra charge.</p>\n<h3>Shipping and customs</h3>\n<p>US shipments are dispatched via <strong>DHL Express or FedEx International Priority</strong> and typically arrive in <strong>7-12 business days</strong>. We provide a commercial invoice, HS code declaration (HS 9705 for trophies/awards), packing list, and country-of-origin certificate with every shipment. US Customs may assess import duties on commercial shipments — consult CBP.gov or your local customs broker for specific tariff rates applicable.</p>\n<p>To order, WhatsApp us at <strong>+91 9480150888</strong> or email <strong>merutrophy@gmail.com</strong> with your trophy type, quantity, engraving text, and US delivery address. We accept bank transfers (SWIFT), Wise international transfers, and can discuss other payment options.</p>"
